            {
              "content": "=nalyze the following learning material and create a structured summary.\n\n**Title:** {{ $json.title }}\n\n**Content:**\n{{ $json.content }}\n\n**Instructions:**\n1. Extract 5-7 key points (most important takeaways)\n2. Identify 3-5 main concepts (core ideas to understand)\n3. Assess difficulty level: beginner, intermediate, or advanced\n4. Provide a brief overview (2-3 sentences)\n\n**Output format (JSON):**\n{\n  \"title\": \"extracted or improved title\",\n  \"overview\": \"brief 2-3 sentence summary\",\n  \"keyPoints\": [\n    \"First key point\",\n    \"Second key point\",\n    ...\n  ],\n  \"mainConcepts\": [\n    \"First concept\",\n    \"Second concept\",\n    ...\n  ],\n  \"difficulty\": \"beginner|intermediate|advanced\",\n  \"estimatedReadingTime\": \"X minutes\"\n}\n\nReturn ONLY valid JSON, no additional text."
